{"tid":604081,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【719】新華製藥夥阿里 拓大數據等合作","createTime":"2018-03-24T11:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T11:02:09.000Z","uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a4bd2795d15dc9f38418398e0a148c80f67d3f2c","tid":604081,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T11:02:09.000Z","msg":"星島日報<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】山東新華製藥(00719)與阿里巴巴簽署框架合作協議，將在B2B業務、雲計算、大數據、新零售、採購平台等領域，展開深入合作。<br />\n　　同時，雙方還通過簽署子協議，推進重點合作內容的深入發展<br />\n　　阿里巴巴集團副總裁楊猛表示，非常感謝新華製藥對阿里的信任，希望打造成與醫藥企業合作的標桿和樣本。(nc)<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/719-新華製藥夥阿里-拓大數據等合作-032700883--finance.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Ffinance%2F719-%E6%96%B0%E8%8F%AF%E8%A3%BD%E8%97%A5%E5%A4%A5%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C-%E6%8B%93%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E7%AD%89%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-032700883--finance.html&d=4P%2FVYxtlXed%2B3naUXCYKwf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=4bb3ceaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/719-新華製藥夥阿里-拓大數據等合作-032700883--finance.html</a>"}]}